Intro:
This program converts a hOCR file into a corpus that can be opened in poliqarp (http://poliqarp.sourceforge.net/).
It treats information about fonts as grammatical categories, enabling a user to query the corpus by these information.

Usage:
./font_sensitive.py hOCR_filename [corpus_name]

Requirements:
bpng (poliqarp.sourceforge.net/man/bpng.html) must be installed

